What it does

  This app allows you to see in an easy way how healthy your fast food meals are, select a restaurant, the meals you might
  be interested in, and get an simple and interactive chart that color-codes them depending on their calories and healtyness.

Contributors

  Kathleen Chalas; Francisco Ribes Clerigues; Siddharth Bhaduri; Alhaji Mansaray; Clarence Elliott;
  Matthew Falkenhainer

Installation

  1-Download the .apk on your phone or tablet
  2-Set your phone or tablet to allow apps from unknown sources(Setings->Security) 
  3-install .apk
